- Learning outcomes: []
- Previous session context: No previous session context provided.
- Learning pace: Balanced
- Preferred difficulty: Balanced
- Output language: Hindi
- Language execution rule: Write every natural-language value in Hindi. Keep JSON keys, ids, schema property names, enum-like structural labels, and DB-facing keys in English. Do not switch explanatory text, questions, answers, titles, instructions, speaker notes, or summaries back to English when Hindi is required.

